I can't help but think about it.

276
00:27:11,500 --> 00:27:13,500
Because you were born in the Song family,

277
00:27:18,500 --> 00:27:20,500
so you have to follow me.

278
00:27:21,500 --> 00:27:22,500
Otherwise,

279
00:27:24,500 --> 00:27:26,500
you could have follow your heart more.

280
00:27:30,500 --> 00:27:32,500
You are my son,

281
00:27:33,500 --> 00:27:36,500
that's why you have to bear everything of our family.

282
00:27:39,500 --> 00:27:41,500
You must really hate this house.

283
00:27:42,500 --> 00:27:44,500
I never thought that.

284
00:27:46,500 --> 00:27:50,500
I understand that you and Mother are worried about me.

285
00:27:54,500 --> 00:27:55,500
Father.

286
00:27:56,500 --> 00:27:58,500
don't worry.

287
00:28:00,500 --> 00:28:02,500
When the day of the general meeting comes,

288
00:28:04,500 --> 00:28:06,500
everything will be alright.

289
00:28:25,500 --> 00:28:26,500
Thanks a lot

290
00:28:27,500 --> 00:28:28,500
for your sacrifice.

291
00:29:03,500 --> 00:29:04,500
You're late again, Yang.

292
00:29:06,500 --> 00:29:07,500
Do you see that everyone is waiting for you?

293
00:29:09,500 --> 00:29:13,500
Don't scold him, Father. Today is a good day.

294
00:29:16,500 --> 00:29:19,500
That's right, our family is having good news.

295
00:29:19,800 --> 00:29:20,500
Don't scold him.

296
00:29:24,500 --> 00:29:26,500
Good news? What good news?

297
00:29:27,500 --> 00:29:29,500
I'm getting married.

298
00:29:35,500 --> 00:29:36,500
Really?

299
00:29:37,500 --> 00:29:38,500
Yeah.

300
00:29:40,500 --> 00:29:43,500
Getting married quickly. Don't know what other plans you have.

301
00:29:46,500 --> 00:29:47,500
Madam.

302
00:29:48,500 --> 00:29:49,500
Don't say that.

303
00:29:50,500 --> 00:29:53,500
Mr. Song is not feeling well. The doctor doesn't want him to be stressed.

304
00:29:57,500 --> 00:29:58,500
Let's eat.

305
00:30:00,500 --> 00:30:01,500
Sir.

306
00:30:01,800 --> 00:30:02,500
Thanks.

307
00:30:59,500 --> 00:31:02,500
Zhang Zhitian.

308
00:31:12,500 --> 00:31:14,500
Zhang, Zhang, Zhang.

309
00:31:15,000 --> 00:31:15,500
Zhang.

310
00:31:16,500 --> 00:31:23,500
I'd like you to know the pain I got,

311
00:31:25,500 --> 00:31:31,500
so that you can understand how I feel.

312
00:31:40,500 --> 00:31:42,500
Bao said that you're here.

313
00:31:51,500 --> 00:31:53,500
Spirit tablet of Mr. Zhang.

314
00:31:54,500 --> 00:31:56,500
What are you thinking?

315
00:31:57,500 --> 00:31:59,500
I'm thinking about that day

316
00:32:01,500 --> 00:32:04,500
when Zhang committed suicide in front of me.

317
00:32:05,500 --> 00:32:08,500
But it's been a long time.

318
00:32:09,500 --> 00:32:10,500
No matter how long it is,

319
00:32:13,500 --> 00:32:14,500
I never forget.

320
00:32:24,500 --> 00:32:28,500
His eyes and his words towards me,

321
00:32:31,500 --> 00:32:33,500
it sounds very painful.

322
00:32:36,500 --> 00:32:38,500
It always echoes in my head.

323
00:32:41,500 --> 00:32:42,500
I didn't know

324
00:32:44,500 --> 00:32:46,500
how much he suffered,

325
00:32:48,500 --> 00:32:50,500
so that he decided to do so.

326
00:32:56,500 --> 00:32:57,500
Sir.

327
00:33:31,500 --> 00:33:32,500
Tian.

328
00:33:36,500 --> 00:33:37,500
Yang.

329
00:33:39,500 --> 00:33:42,500
Are you really going to get married?

330
00:33:46,500 --> 00:33:47,500
Why?

331
00:33:51,500 --> 00:33:53,500
I made up my mind already.

332
00:34:08,064 --> 00:34:09,648
Look at this first.

333
00:34:10,272 --> 00:34:13,500
You may consider about the wedding again.

334
00:34:50,336 --> 00:34:51,500
Tian.

335
00:34:53,616 --> 00:34:55,760
I want to explain everything.

336
00:34:57,960 --> 00:35:00,128
I have to work for Mr. Ma

337
00:35:01,176 --> 00:35:04,500
because he told me he had medicine for Mei's illness.

338
00:35:05,424 --> 00:35:07,216
But I just found out

339
00:35:08,168 --> 00:35:10,344
that the medicine is opium.

340
00:35:12,500 --> 00:35:14,160
I'm really stupid.

341
00:35:16,400 --> 00:35:18,360
I can't help my sister and brother.

342
00:35:20,032 --> 00:35:22,128
I also hurt you.

343
00:35:24,760 --> 00:35:26,500
I'm sorry.

344
00:35:29,320 --> 00:35:31,936
Please come to meet me tomorrow.

345
00:35:32,592 --> 00:35:35,152
I'll tell you everything

346
00:35:36,968 --> 00:35:38,880
and let's run away together.

347
00:35:51,720 --> 00:35:53,736
I love you, Tian.

348
00:36:52,840 --> 00:36:54,040
Mr. Yang.

349
00:36:54,416 --> 00:36:56,128
Didn't Tian come with you?

350
00:37:05,864 --> 00:37:08,072
He let me give you this letter.

351
00:37:33,464 --> 00:37:36,080
I can't meet you as you said.

352
00:37:36,752 --> 00:37:39,264
It's not that I don't love you

353
00:37:39,272 --> 00:37:41,688
or still angry about Mr. Ma.

354
00:37:42,720 --> 00:37:45,168
I understand that you have a reason.

355
00:37:45,656 --> 00:37:47,256
If it were me,

356
00:37:47,488 --> 00:37:50,120
I may choose to do the same thing.

357
00:37:50,800 --> 00:37:52,104
Jiu.

358
00:37:53,352 --> 00:37:58,440
The two of us are lucky but not enough to be together.

359
00:37:59,024 --> 00:38:01,992
What we've been through together

360
00:38:02,216 --> 00:38:04,584
made me know what love is.

361
00:38:04,760 --> 00:38:09,024
It taught me that there's someone who really loves me like you in this world.

362
00:38:10,712 --> 00:38:13,320
But in this world, it's not just the two of us.

363
00:38:14,672 --> 00:38:16,936
I have a duty to do

364
00:38:17,256 --> 00:38:19,488
and I couldn't leave it.

365
00:38:20,640 --> 00:38:22,944
I've made up my mind carefully.

366
00:38:23,464 --> 00:38:26,936
Please believe in what I choose to do.

367
00:38:28,448 --> 00:38:29,688
Lastly,

368
00:38:30,416 --> 00:38:32,416
I will miss you.

369
00:38:33,656 --> 00:38:37,032
I will keep you in my memory forever.

370
00:38:37,752 --> 00:38:39,904
I hope you miss me too.

371
00:39:35,120 --> 00:39:36,728
What's wrong?

372
00:39:38,216 --> 00:39:39,760
Is this Tian's letter?

373
00:39:40,456 --> 00:39:42,480
What did he say?

374
00:39:44,376 --> 00:39:46,952
Tian said he wouldn't see us again, Mei.

375
00:39:47,448 --> 00:39:48,800
Why?

376
00:39:49,100 --> 00:39:51,720
Didn't you say you two love each other?

377
00:39:51,736 --> 00:39:53,624
Why are you not together?

378
00:39:58,950 --> 00:40:00,950
He had already chosen his path.

379
00:40:02,950 --> 00:40:03,950
We must go our way.

380
00:40:08,950 --> 00:40:09,950
Mei.

381
00:40:10,950 --> 00:40:13,950
I'll go pick up Fu, then let's get out of here.

382
00:42:06,950 --> 00:42:07,950
We agree to cooperate with you

383
00:42:08,950 --> 00:42:12,950
because I think you won't break the promise you made to us

384
00:42:13,950 --> 00:42:17,950
that you'll sell all the goods from your association, including oil and rice

385
00:42:18,950 --> 00:42:20,950
to us at the price three times lower than the market price.

386
00:42:22,950 --> 00:42:25,950
If you can't do it, you know what's going to happen, right?

387
00:42:26,950 --> 00:42:27,950
I know it.

388
00:42:28,950 --> 00:42:32,950
If only I can take the head position of Five Dragons Association,

389
00:42:34,950 --> 00:42:38,950
I'll determine the price of all products.

390
00:42:39,950 --> 00:42:42,950
I will sell products to Japanese soldiers at cheap prices.

391
00:42:43,650 --> 00:42:46,950
I will raise the purchase price from the villagers.

392
00:42:47,950 --> 00:42:49,950
I can only see profits now.

393
00:42:50,250 --> 00:42:50,950
Great.

394
00:42:51,950 --> 00:42:53,950
So we'll have the soldiers ready.

395
00:42:54,950 --> 00:42:55,950
When you want to use them, just let me know.

396
00:42:57,950 --> 00:43:01,950
In a few days, there will be a big meeting at the Five Dragons Association.

397
00:43:02,950 --> 00:43:07,950
I will take the head position of head for myself.

398
00:43:08,950 --> 00:43:09,950
If it turns out to be what I think,

399
00:43:10,950 --> 00:43:12,950
Big Brother will have to do everything

400
00:43:13,950 --> 00:43:16,950
because his son that he expects to inherit his position

401
00:43:17,950 --> 00:43:18,950
has done something embarrassing.

402
00:43:19,950 --> 00:43:25,950
But if they are stubborn, I need to request Japanese troops from you

403
00:43:26,950 --> 00:43:27,950
to get rid of them, Captain.

404
00:43:28,950 --> 00:43:30,950
Don't worry.

405
00:43:31,950 --> 00:43:35,950
No matter how big or powerful Mr. Song is,

406
00:43:36,950 --> 00:43:40,950
if he has a fight with Japanese soldiers,

407
00:43:41,950 --> 00:43:44,950
Thai authorities or anyone won't dare to help him.

408
00:43:46,950 --> 00:43:47,950
Good.

409
00:43:51,950 --> 00:43:52,950
Hey who is it?

410
00:43:56,950 --> 00:43:57,950
Gui.

411
00:43:58,250 --> 00:43:58,950
It's Jiu, Sir.

412
00:44:08,950 --> 00:44:09,950
Shoot him.

413
00:44:24,950 --> 00:44:25,950
Watch out, Sir.

414
00:44:28,950 --> 00:44:29,950
Hey, he ran away!

415
00:44:30,250 --> 00:44:31,950
Catch him! Hurry!

416
00:44:32,550 --> 00:44:32,950
Yes, Sir. Go.

417
00:44:59,950 --> 00:45:00,950
Fu.

418
00:45:01,950 --> 00:45:02,950
Fu, Fu.

419
00:45:03,250 --> 00:45:03,950
Fu.

420
00:45:04,950 --> 00:45:05,950
Fu.

421
00:45:07,950 --> 00:45:08,950
Fu, Fu.

422
00:45:09,950 --> 00:45:10,950
Fu.

423
00:45:11,950 --> 00:45:12,950
Fu.

424
00:45:14,950 --> 00:45:16,950
I'm here to help you. You're alright.

425
00:45:28,950 --> 00:45:29,950
Jiu.

426
00:45:33,950 --> 00:45:34,950
Let's hurry up, Fu. Let's go.

427
00:45:38,950 --> 00:45:40,950
Hey, stop! Where are you taking the kid?

428
00:45:46,950 --> 00:45:47,950
Let's go, Fu.

429
00:45:48,350 --> 00:45:48,950
Stop.

430
00:45:54,950 --> 00:45:58,950
This route is the route that Mr. Ma regularly uses to come here.

431
00:45:59,950 --> 00:46:00,950
Passing this intersection, there is a forest.

432
00:46:02,950 --> 00:46:03,950
Shall we attack him here, Madam?

433
00:46:05,950 --> 00:46:07,950
It's true that not many people pass by here.

434
00:46:08,950 --> 00:46:09,950
But it is a dense forest.

435
00:46:10,550 --> 00:46:12,950
The two of us may not be able to fight men that much.

436
00:46:13,950 --> 00:46:15,950
If Mr. Ma runs away,

437
00:46:16,250 --> 00:46:18,950
there can be many places to hide. It'll be hard for us to look for him.

438
00:46:22,950 --> 00:46:23,950
Better take this way.

439
00:46:24,950 --> 00:46:27,950
There aren't a lot of people passing by.

440
00:46:28,950 --> 00:46:30,950
But it's a sparse forest. It should be convenient for escaping.

441
00:46:35,950 --> 00:46:37,950
I hope everything works out.

442
00:46:38,950 --> 00:46:39,950
Please don't let anything go wrong.

443
00:46:40,950 --> 00:46:42,950
About both Mr. Ma

444
00:46:43,950 --> 00:46:44,950
and Jiu.

445
00:46:46,950 --> 00:46:50,950
Regarding Jiu, don't worry.

446
00:46:51,950 --> 00:46:54,950
He's a human, not a stone. He has to move his body.

447
00:46:55,950 --> 00:46:59,950
Perhaps he is fleeing somewhere right now.

448
00:47:00,950 --> 00:47:03,950
But the more he runs away, the more tired he'll be.

449
00:47:04,950 --> 00:47:06,950
The more he moves, the closer he is to death.

450
00:47:07,950 --> 00:47:09,950
The poison of orchid will slowly get into the blood

451
00:47:10,950 --> 00:47:12,950
and suck his blood.

452
00:47:13,950 --> 00:47:16,950
The one who is exposed to it will begin to suffocate.

453
00:47:17,450 --> 00:47:18,950
Eventually he coughs up blood and dies.

454
00:47:29,950 --> 00:47:30,950
Fu, quickly.

455
00:47:39,950 --> 00:47:40,950
Let's go.

456
00:47:42,950 --> 00:47:43,950
What's the matter?

457
00:47:45,950 --> 00:47:46,950
Jiu.

458
00:47:48,950 --> 00:47:50,950
Jiu, Jiu.

459
00:47:51,450 --> 00:47:53,950
What's wrong with you? Jiu.

460
00:47:54,250 --> 00:47:54,950
Jiu.

461
00:47:59,950 --> 00:48:01,950
They're almost here.

462
00:48:03,950 --> 00:48:05,950
Fu, run away quickly. Don't worry about me.

463
00:48:06,250 --> 00:48:06,950
Ni.

464
00:48:07,150 --> 00:48:08,950
Go, I told you to go. Go! / No, no.

465
00:48:09,150 --> 00:48:10,950
Go! Just go! Hurry!

466
00:48:42,950 --> 00:48:44,950
You two go catch the child.

467
00:48:45,250 --> 00:48:46,950
You come with me.

468
00:49:31,950 --> 00:49:32,950
Where did he go?

469
00:49:34,950 --> 00:49:35,950
This way.

470
00:50:30,950 --> 00:50:31,950
Where is he?

471
00:50:32,250 --> 00:50:32,950
I don't know.

472
00:50:33,150 --> 00:50:33,950
Let's go that way.

473
00:50:56,950 --> 00:50:57,950
Where did he go?

474
00:51:06,950 --> 00:51:08,950
Let's find him, he can't go too far.

475
00:51:44,950 --> 00:51:45,950
Officer.

476
00:51:48,950 --> 00:51:53,950
I'm here to give you a clue about a worker named Dong who died in the Song family.

477
00:52:17,950 --> 00:52:19,950
Even if I announce the marriage,

478
00:52:21,950 --> 00:52:23,950
Father will never stop suspecting.

479
00:52:26,950 --> 00:52:31,950
he will know one day that you have poison that is used to kill people.

480
00:52:33,950 --> 00:52:34,950
And if that day comes,

481
00:52:36,950 --> 00:52:37,950
what are you going to do?

482
00:52:38,950 --> 00:52:40,950
I have a solution.

483
00:52:44,950 --> 00:52:45,950
I know that.

484
00:52:47,950 --> 00:52:50,950
I must pay for killing someone.

485
00:52:53,950 --> 00:52:54,950
But I can do everything

486
00:52:57,950 --> 00:53:00,950
to make you get through this

487
00:53:01,950 --> 00:53:03,950
and get the position of association head.

488
00:53:12,950 --> 00:53:13,950
Yang.

489
00:53:16,950 --> 00:53:17,950
Did you follow me here?

490
00:53:19,950 --> 00:53:22,950
I'm wondering what exactly you are doing.

491
00:53:24,950 --> 00:53:25,950
Nothing.

492
00:53:26,250 --> 00:53:28,950
Nothing? Then why are you here?

493
00:53:30,950 --> 00:53:33,950
Hey, you're not alone.

494
00:53:34,950 --> 00:53:36,950
Tell me so I can help you fix it.

495
00:53:37,950 --> 00:53:39,950
I finished everything.

496
00:53:41,950 --> 00:53:42,950
You're not going to tell me?

497
00:53:43,950 --> 00:53:44,950
If you don't, I'll go ask the police myself.

498
00:53:45,950 --> 00:53:47,950
Yang, Yang.

499
00:53:48,250 --> 00:53:48,950
Brother.

500
00:53:49,950 --> 00:53:50,950
Fu.

501
00:53:51,950 --> 00:53:53,950
Tian, please help me.

502
00:54:04,950 --> 00:54:06,950
Jiu said that he would pick up Fu.

503
00:54:07,950 --> 00:54:11,950
But he disappeared all night and hasn't returned yet.

504
00:54:13,950 --> 00:54:14,950
It's alright, Mei.

505
00:54:15,950 --> 00:54:16,950
He'll come back soon.

506
00:54:19,950 --> 00:54:21,950
Yang, Tian.

507
00:54:22,950 --> 00:54:23,950
Fu. / Mei.

508
00:54:28,950 --> 00:54:30,950
Mei said that Jiu went to help his brother out.

509
00:54:31,950 --> 00:54:33,950
And where is he?

510
00:54:38,950 --> 00:54:42,950
Jiu…Jiu is dead.

511
00:54:56,950 --> 00:54:58,950
Fu, let me ask you.

512
00:54:59,950 --> 00:55:02,950
What happened last night. Is Jiu really dead?

513
00:55:03,950 --> 00:55:08,950
Last night, he saved me, but was caught by Mr. Ma.

514
00:55:09,350 --> 00:55:10,950
So he let me run away first.

515
00:55:11,950 --> 00:55:15,950
Jiu is dead, Mei. Jiu is dead.

516
00:56:52,950 --> 00:56:53,950
I saw someone sneaked into the house.

517
00:56:54,950 --> 00:56:56,950
I'm afraid he will hurt you.

518
00:57:09,950 --> 00:57:13,950
You can hate me for being this.

519
00:57:14,950 --> 00:57:16,950
I never hate you.

520
00:57:26,950 --> 00:57:27,950
I love you, Tian.

521
00:57:45,950 --> 00:57:50,950
I already know. A scum like you do everything for money.

522
00:57:52,950 --> 00:57:53,950
Don't let me see your face again.

523
00:57:54,950 --> 00:57:56,950
Tian, listen to me first.

524
00:57:57,950 --> 00:57:58,950
Go away.

525
00:58:02,950 --> 00:58:04,950
No, I'm not leaving.

526
00:58:07,950 --> 00:58:08,950
Go!

527
00:58:49,950 --> 00:58:50,950
Tian.

528
00:58:52,950 --> 00:58:53,950
Yang.

529
00:58:55,950 --> 00:58:56,950
Jiu…

530
00:59:00,950 --> 00:59:02,950
Jiu is dead.

531
00:59:04,950 --> 00:59:05,950
Tian.

532
00:59:11,950 --> 00:59:14,950
Parting is better than death.

533
00:59:17,950 --> 00:59:22,950
At least I still know that he is somewhere living a happy life.

534
00:59:27,950 --> 00:59:29,950
But he is dead.

535
00:59:31,950 --> 00:59:33,950
Last time we met,

536
00:59:37,950 --> 00:59:38,950
I spoke badly to him.

537
00:59:40,950 --> 00:59:41,950
Tian.

538
00:59:44,950 --> 00:59:45,950
Listen to me.

539
00:59:50,950 --> 00:59:51,950
At least,

540
00:59:53,950 --> 00:59:56,950
you lived happily with him once.

541
00:59:59,950 --> 01:00:00,950
I believe...

542
01:00:01,950 --> 01:00:06,950
that he could feel how much you loved him.

543
01:00:13,950 --> 01:00:14,950
It's okay.

544
01:00:16,950 --> 01:00:19,950
Destiny brought us together up until here.

545
01:00:29,950 --> 01:00:30,950
Yang.

546
01:00:36,950 --> 01:00:38,950
Fate brought Mei and Fu to meet us.

547
01:00:47,950 --> 01:00:52,950
Can you and Pin take care of that two of them for me?

548
01:00:57,950 --> 01:00:58,950
Tian.

549
01:01:01,950 --> 01:01:02,950
Why do you say this?

550
01:01:04,950 --> 01:01:05,950
Where are you going?

551
01:01:10,950 --> 01:01:12,950
I have a duty to do.

552
01:01:28,950 --> 01:01:31,950
Our people didn't find Jiu, Sir.

553
01:01:32,650 --> 01:01:33,950
And where did that bastard go?

554
01:01:34,650 --> 01:01:35,950
We didn't see his body?

555
01:01:36,250 --> 01:01:36,950
Right, Sir.

556
01:01:37,350 --> 01:01:39,950
If Jiu is not dead and helps Tian when we expose him,

557
01:01:40,950 --> 01:01:42,950
what should we do, magnate?

558
01:01:44,950 --> 01:01:48,950
Inform Captain Hiroshi, requesting for Japanese troops to help us tomorrow.

559
01:01:49,950 --> 01:01:53,950
If you can't use soft way, we have to do this the hard way.

560
01:01:55,950 --> 01:01:56,950
Yes, Sir.

561
01:01:57,450 --> 01:01:57,950
Go.

562
01:02:12,950 --> 01:02:15,950
May God protect our family.

563
01:02:16,950 --> 01:02:20,950
Please let tomorrow's ceremony go well.

564
01:02:21,950 --> 01:02:24,950
Tomorrow is a good day, an auspicious day

565
01:02:25,950 --> 01:02:27,950
Everything must go smoothly, Sir.

566
01:03:01,950 --> 01:03:04,950
Tomorrow before the ceremony starts, we have to stop Mr. Ma.

567
01:03:05,950 --> 01:03:07,950
Kill him before he arrives.

568
01:03:09,950 --> 01:03:12,950
Mr. Ma has absolutely no way of exposing Mr. Tian.

569
01:03:13,950 --> 01:03:15,950
Everything will be fine, Madam.

570
01:03:36,950 --> 01:03:38,950
You look gorgeous today, Mud.

571
01:03:39,950 --> 01:03:40,950
You have to call her madam.

572
01:03:41,950 --> 01:03:43,950
She is about to marry Mr. Tian.

573
01:03:44,350 --> 01:03:44,950
You're lucky.

574
01:03:45,950 --> 01:03:46,950
Thanks.

575
01:03:52,950 --> 01:03:55,950
Oh, you finish getting dressed?

576
01:03:56,250 --> 01:03:57,950
I thought of going to help you.

577
01:03:58,950 --> 01:04:01,950
Mud, you go get ready. The ceremony is beginning soon.

578
01:04:02,950 --> 01:04:03,950
Yes, Sir.

579
01:04:12,950 --> 01:04:15,950
Wish the ceremony would be thwarted.

580
01:04:16,250 --> 01:04:16,950
Mom.

581
01:04:21,950 --> 01:04:24,950
After everyone is here at an auspicious time,

582
01:04:25,950 --> 01:04:28,950
the ceremony will begin by paying respect to the ancestral spirit tablets over there.

583
01:04:29,950 --> 01:04:33,950
After it's done, the meeting of the association will begin.

584
01:04:34,550 --> 01:04:37,950
Once the results of the annual trade have been reported,

585
01:04:38,950 --> 01:04:42,950
you can announce that Mr. Tian is getting married

586
01:04:43,950 --> 01:04:46,950
and then give the workers money envelopes.

587
01:04:48,950 --> 01:04:50,950
Do you have anything you want to add?

588
01:04:51,950 --> 01:04:53,950
Let me think.

589
01:04:54,450 --> 01:04:55,950
If I want something, I'll let you know.

590
01:04:56,350 --> 01:04:56,950
Yes, Sir.

591
01:04:58,950 --> 01:04:59,950
Is there anything that...

592
01:05:00,250 --> 01:05:00,950
Madam.

593
01:05:01,150 --> 01:05:01,950
Madam. / Li.

594
01:05:02,950 --> 01:05:03,950
Madam. / Li.

595
01:05:04,150 --> 01:05:04,950
Madam faints.

596
01:05:05,950 --> 01:05:08,950
Don't gather here. Go get a fan and an inhaler quickly.

597
01:05:09,950 --> 01:05:10,950
Bring some tea. Tea.

598
01:05:14,950 --> 01:05:18,950
Captain Hiroshi said that he would send a force to join us at Mr. Song's house.

599
01:05:19,950 --> 01:05:22,950
But he insisted that no one should know about his support.

600
01:05:38,950 --> 01:05:39,950
Jia.

601
01:05:40,950 --> 01:05:41,950
Did you call the doctor?

602
01:05:42,950 --> 01:05:43,950
It's okay, Sir.

603
01:05:44,550 --> 01:05:47,950
Madam might not have got enough sleep, so is feeling dizzy. Having some rest will do.

604
01:05:48,950 --> 01:05:52,950
Madam is sick. Should we notify the cancellation of Tian's ceremony first?

605
01:05:53,150 --> 01:05:53,950
Because the right time has passed.

606
01:05:54,250 --> 01:05:54,950
Mom.

607
01:05:55,950 --> 01:05:57,950
Don't do that, please.

608
01:05:58,950 --> 01:06:01,950
If Madam sleeps for a while, she will recover just in time.

609
01:06:03,950 --> 01:06:06,950
Everyone, please leave. I'll take care of her myself.

610
01:06:07,950 --> 01:06:08,950
I leave her to you, Jia.

611
01:06:09,450 --> 01:06:09,950
Yes, Sir.

612
01:06:35,950 --> 01:06:36,950
They're gone, Madam.

613
01:07:07,950 --> 01:07:08,950
Why you stop?

614
01:07:09,950 --> 01:07:12,950
There's a fallen tree blocking the road. We can't get through it.

615
01:07:16,950 --> 01:07:18,950
Then turn left, there's a shortcut.

616
01:07:19,950 --> 01:07:20,950
Yes, Sir.

617
01:07:55,950 --> 01:07:56,950
What's wrong?

618
01:07:57,950 --> 01:07:58,950
I suspect the tire leaks.

619
01:08:09,950 --> 01:08:10,950
What the hell?

620
01:08:57,950 --> 01:08:58,950
Jia.

621
01:09:02,950 --> 01:09:03,950
Gui.

622
01:09:16,950 --> 01:09:17,950
Jia.

623
01:09:34,950 --> 01:09:35,950
I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

624
01:09:36,950 --> 01:09:38,950
I made a mistake, I'm sorry. I won't do it again.

625
01:09:39,950 --> 01:09:42,950
I'm sorry. I'm sorry. I'm really sorry.

626
01:10:24,950 --> 01:10:25,950
Li.

627
01:11:18,950 --> 01:11:21,950
It's done. He won't survive.

628
01:11:56,950 --> 01:11:58,950
I love you, Tian.

629
01:13:08,950 --> 01:13:09,950
Everything

630
01:13:12,950 --> 01:13:13,950
must end today.

631
01:13:51,950 --> 01:13:53,950
What should we do next?

632
01:13:59,950 --> 01:14:01,950
I've made up my mind, Yang.

633
01:14:02,950 --> 01:14:04,950
Take care of Father and Mother, okay?
